data.description: Discover your dream home! This charming light brick house on a spacious corner lot offers both comfort and luxury. With RV parking and lush trees providing privacy, you’ll feel secluded yet conveniently located. Inside, you can find four bedrooms, two bathrooms, and a semi-open split floor plan. The kitchen boasts new countertops, backsplash and appliances, including a refrigerator  that will convey with the property. Enjoy the enclosed sunroom and safe room for relaxation and security. Step outsiders to a backyard oasis featuring a heated and cooled pool house with an outdoor bar, an above-ground pool, turfed yard, covered grilling area and a putting green! The perfect place for any summer gathering! Don’t miss out - schedule your viewing today and make this your forever home!
